  "design_notes": "A well-structured and highly intuitive Easy chart tailored for a 4-panel dance pad. The chart features a sparse intro pacing the player, leading into active drops on quarter-note downbeats with comfortable holds (sharing exactly ~12% of the steps, within budget). No crossovers, footswitches, or jacks are used to ensure maximum casual flow. The highest energy drop climax around bars 26-34 features steady 4th notes that trace the musical energy beautifully, peaking around 2.53 NPS.",
